{"type": "article", "id": 23530, "title": "黄白圆点啤酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-09T07:30:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104148M9RgWfr8YlDtPcSm.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款啤酒的特别版包装，主要采用了白黄相间的圆点图案，清新而亮丽。酒瓶是传统的棕色半透明的琥珀瓶，白色的贴纸上出现了黄色半圆形图案和图案作为底色，从正面看，文字和图案又配合成了一个娃娃的笑脸，黑色的 VINCIT 像是眼睛，图标作为鼻子，下面也有一串细长的弧形文字作为嘴巴，很俏皮。另外，配合这套啤酒包装拍摄的宣传图也很漂亮。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104146Rlpzynd7MKm4jCsA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104146qbwaImBH4p35KG8y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104146E63QKJ4FXfa0UsTu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104147aQXf23p0nFRULHIG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104147sNhUrdc8A2HZx9fL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}